            p.demo__description Based on
                a.demo__link(href = "https://dribble.com") this dribble shot
            | by Gal Shir
        div(class = "demo__section demo__section--demos")
            h2.demo__section-heading 3Д Резьба(металл, дерево)
            p.demo__description Check my
                a.demo__link(href = "https://dribble.com") other demos
            
        div(class = "demo__section demo__section--about")
            h2.demo__section-heading Стрижка собак
            p.demo__description 
                a.demo__link(href = "http://rudik.info") this site

        div(class = "demo__section demo__section--contacts")
            h2.demo__section-heading Ришельевская 6, кв.7
            p.demo__description как шутили в Одессе
                a.demo__link(href = "http://rudik.info") this site
            
